*php-7.0.4-r1 (21 Mar 2016)

  21 Mar 2016; Michael Orlitzky <mjo@gentoo.org> -php-7.0.4.ebuild,
  +php-7.0.4-r1.ebuild:
  revision the 7.0 series to add pdo-dblib support.

  The PDO "dblib" driver was somehow lost during the transition from
  php:5.6 to php:7.0. I've added it back, and tested that it works with
  a simple query against a Microsoft SQL Server 2005 database.

  Gentoo-Bug: 576782

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

  21 Mar 2016; Michael Orlitzky <mjo@gentoo.org> -php-5.5.30.ebuild,
  -php-5.6.14.ebuild:
  remove vulnerable php-5.5.30 and php-5.6.14.

  Gentoo-Bug: 571254

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

  24 Mar 2016; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> php-5.5.33.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #577376

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28
  RepoMan-Options: --include-arches="arm"

  24 Mar 2016; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> php-5.6.19.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #577376

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28
  RepoMan-Options: --include-arches="arm"

  24 Mar 2016; Michael Orlitzky <mjo@gentoo.org> -php-5.5.31.ebuild,
