*php-7.0.9-r1 (26 Jul 2016)
*php-5.6.24-r1 (26 Jul 2016)

  26 Jul 2016; Michael Orlitzky <mjo@gentoo.org> +php-5.6.24-r1.ebuild,
  +php-7.0.9-r1.ebuild:
  new 5.6 and 7.0 revisions to clean up metadata cruft.

  The SRC_URI handling in our current ebuilds was a bit
  over-complicated. I've reorganized all of the metadata (KEYWORDS,
  SRC_URI, etc.) so that it's easier to understand. There were also some
  superfluous environment variables that have been removed.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28

  26 Jul 2016; Michael Orlitzky <mjo@gentoo.org> -files/php5-ldvs:
  remove unused file ${FILESDIR}/php5-ldvs.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28

  27 Jul 2016; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> php-7.0.9-r1.ebuild:
  Whitespace

  Package-Manager: portage-2.3.0

